title: TUESDAY 1/26 - Kelce causing headaches
itunes:title: TUESDAY 1/26 - Kelce causing headaches
description:
The ageless wonder Tom Brady (0:06) set to play in his 10th career Super Bowl and at the age of 43, Chiefs head coach Andy Reid amazed at what he's able to do (0:40) As for those Chiefs, tight end Travis Kelce (1:04) causing matchup problems for Bruce Arians' Buccaneers (1:19). Josh Allen reflects on the Bills season (2:11) while wide receiver Cole Beasley reveals the extent of a leg issue that would've shut down most players (2:43). Plus, we'll take a look at the latest coaching moves around the league (3:08)
